title: A home with a personal touch - Res Lease in Kyle. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: This beautifully remodeled 3 bed/2 bath located in West Kyle is available and ready for immediate move in!
Sitting on a huge lot in a cul-de-sac, you'll love this home from the moment you walk in.
The wood-burning fireplace is the center of attention as you walk into the large living room.
With a split floor plan, the primary bedroom is in the back of the home while the other 2 bedrooms are towards the front.
All the bedrooms are large, and one could make a great front office.
Updates throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, you have 2 walk in showers, a huge walk-in closet in the primary bedroom, as well as a walk out door to the back patio from the primary bedroom.
The large back yard is complete with a storage shed and covered wrap around patio.
Please call or text Listing Agent 2 - Tyler Zimmerman - for all questions or for showings.
Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.
Listed By: Talitha Pierceson, Realty One Group Prosper
